                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/137.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to chargé
                            <persName type="to">O’Shaughnessy</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-12-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 8, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your December 6. You are instructed to bring to attention of appropriate
                    authorities any illegal procedure in connection with the levying of taxes in
                    Sinaloa.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
